{"tid":2061781,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"將831視為\"黑警日\", 唔好比後人忘記","createTime":"2020-06-12T15:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T16:32:49.000Z","uid":100596,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b05f61ec627ecc41cf709427423abd009ebbed4f","tid":2061781,"uid":100596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:42:43.000Z","msg":"古人將端午節成為紀念屈原既日子，傳統活動有食糉，爬龍舟，一直傳統至今。<br />\n<br />\n秦儈受到民間廣泛痛恨，因而發明油炸鬼，流傳至今; 人民製造秦儈銅像，永世受人唾液。<br />\n<br />\n我忽然有類似既諗法: <br />\n<br />\n以後將831視為&quot;黑警日&quot;，整一d傳統食品，活動，一年傳一年，漸漸成為一個香港傳統日子。<br />\n<br />\n當然唔係紀念班垃圾。而係唔好比香港人忘記呢3萬人曾經既所作所為。未來，當我地後代問起呢d食品，活動時，都知道佢地既歷史，而呢班狗後代永遠都抬唔起頭。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家有咩idea?"},{"pid":"ed17363230c7258dcacaa6375a8adbf7d28592e9","tid":2061781,"uid":41400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:44:09.000Z","msg":"三鰻完蛋飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b2b241012c3e207003aa557f66118f521f86a11","tid":2061781,"uid":140738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:45:20.000Z","msg":"811黑啲定831黑啲"},{"pid":"1ff39fca5c12f223281a9fd61c46ced1ce1d6d5e","tid":2061781,"uid":289978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T15:45:27.000Z","msg":"831 黑警日"},{"pid":"dca6965f8bef59a4052632488952d744bde54bf6","tid":2061781,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:18:29.000Z","msg":"好，支持<br />\n<br />\n下年有人印月曆既可以寫上去"},{"pid":"b4f216ad2cc802dd2abc1b44b01f5f799eabc71c","tid":2061781,"uid":202296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:26:56.000Z","msg":"野食呢個idea幾好<br />\n香港人發揮創意啦喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396e910e4606360364b1e07693d0ec9923ff0b99","tid":2061781,"uid":5499,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T16:32:49.000Z","msg":"建議區議會整個黑警像係18區比人吐口水"}]}